---
// BrandUs.astro
---

<section class="relative w-full mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 lg:px-32 py-16 md:py-32">
    <!-- Background Elements -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10">
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-20 w-72 md:w-96 h-72 md:h-96 bg-accentColor/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-20 right-0 w-52 md:w-72 h-52 md:h-72 bg-accentColor/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
      <div class="absolute -right-20 top-40 w-32 md:w-40 h-32 md:h-40 bg-accentColor/20 rotate-45 blur-2xl"></div>
    </div>
  
    <!-- Header Section -->
    <div class="max-w-4xl mb-12 md:mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white leading-tight">
        Why Ambitious Brands Choose Us For 
        <span class="relative inline-block">
          Unforgettable
          <span class="absolute -bottom-1 md:-bottom-2 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-accentColor/50 blur-sm"></span>
        </span> 
        Digital Experiences
      </h2>
    </div>
  
    <!-- Cards Container -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 md:gap-8">
      <!-- Card 01 -->
      <div class="group p-6 md:p-10 rounded-2xl md:rounded-3xl bg-gray-900/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-800 
                  hover:border-accentColor/50 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4 md:gap-6 mb-4 md:mb-6">
          <span class="font-mono text-accentColor text-base md:text-lg">01.</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3 md:mb-4">
              Tangible results that go beyond expectations
            </h3>
            <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
              We deliver measurable outcomes that exceed your goals. Our data-driven approach ensures 
              that every campaign we undertake not only meets but surpasses your expectations, providing 
              tangible results that truly make a difference to your brand.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
  
      <!-- Card 02 -->
      <div class="group p-6 md:p-10 rounded-2xl md:rounded-3xl bg-gray-900/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-800 
                  hover:border-accentColor/50 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4 md:gap-6 mb-4 md:mb-6">
          <span class="font-mono text-accentColor text-base md:text-lg">02.</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3 md:mb-4">
              Experience in digital marketing services that work
            </h3>
            <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
              With years of expertise in digital marketing, we have honed our skills to offer services 
              that truly work. Our team's deep understanding of evolving digital trends enables us to 
              create effective strategies that resonate with your audience and drive real engagement.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
  
      <!-- Card 03 -->
      <div class="group p-6 md:p-10 rounded-2xl md:rounded-3xl bg-gray-900/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-800 
                  hover:border-accentColor/50 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4 md:gap-6 mb-4 md:mb-6">
          <span class="font-mono text-accentColor text-base md:text-lg">03.</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3 md:mb-4">
              Flexible, adaptable strategies and techniques
            </h3>
            <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
              It's a fast-paced digital world, so adaptability is key. We offer flexible strategies 
              tailored to your unique brand needs, ensuring that no matter how the market shifts, your 
              marketing remains effective. Our dynamic approach allows us to stay ahead of trends and 
              pivot quickly for maximum impact.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
  
      <!-- Card 04 -->
      <div class="group p-6 md:p-10 rounded-2xl md:rounded-3xl bg-gray-900/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-800 
                  hover:border-accentColor/50 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4 md:gap-6 mb-4 md:mb-6">
          <span class="font-mono text-accentColor text-base md:text-lg">04.</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3 md:mb-4">
              Delivering where other agencies struggle
            </h3>
            <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
              Our track record speaks for itself. We've successfully tackled challenges and achieved 
              milestones where others have stumbled. Choosing us means partnering with an agency that 
              has a proven ability to deliver results, even in the most complex and demanding niches 
              and scenarios.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
</section>